{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 274095, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看费曼物理学", "timestamp": 1598017828, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274097, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "先看经济学原理，经济思想史", "timestamp": 1598017861, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274099, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "纯粹理性批判 哲学专业的也看不进去啊。先看看哲学史，报个讨论班，慢慢来。", "timestamp": 1598017928, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看瓦尔登湖", "timestamp": 1598017961, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274103, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "史记看不进去的话或许是文言文的功底不够，先看看近现代历史著作或许会好一点，比如蒋廷黻先生的中国近代史", "timestamp": 1598017986, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274108, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "蛮多慕课资源的，跟着也会有很明显收获的", "timestamp": 1598018033, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 再比如梁启超先生的李鸿章传（eve强推啊啊啊啊啊啊啊），慢慢培养兴趣就好了", "timestamp": 1598018039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274118, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以去跟人文学院的课，这几本书都有开课的", "timestamp": 1598018168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274121, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "比如看康德可以先看道德形而上学的奠基这种嘛，锻炼下文本阅读能力后再深入，以及推荐看看二手文献", "timestamp": 1598018222, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "工科生去年选了哲学系一门读纯粹理性批判的课，读了先验分析论部分，直到写最后的论文时才感觉理清了一点思路（可能因为读的是英文，自己英文阅读太差了）", "timestamp": 1598018331, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 一定先看哲学史！", "timestamp": 1598018342, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274133, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这真的不是在钓鱼吗？？\n为什么这么入门？？", "timestamp": 1598018457, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274157, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以从中国哲学入手，中国古代思想史，再回到西方哲学", "timestamp": 1598018846, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "海德格尔建议尽量不读，康德的话可以去听哲学系范dh老师的课，他是靠谱的年轻学者", "timestamp": 1598019452, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274227, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看卓里奇，这个好懂", "timestamp": 1598020398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274608, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有很多哲学相关的纪录片和公开课都不错，推荐这个crash course，比较有趣味性，可以入门。https://b23.tv/HAOMpD。另外，桑德尔的公开课《正义》也不错：https://b23.tv/68oixB。我个人认为直接读经典对入门来说是很劝退的，每个人都得找些别的感兴趣自己的方式慢慢深入～有了追问以后，就会自然而然引导你读经典啦", "timestamp": 1598026285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274617, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 这学期哲学系范dh老师开了道德形而上学奠基呢，感兴趣的同学一起去上呀。（研究生课开的是实践理性批判", "timestamp": 1598026637, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274734, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "既然范老师又开《奠基》，那么强推。本科时上过他这门课，感觉不熟悉康德的人首先通过《奠基》来接近他是比较好的选择（至少书不厚不那么劝退", "timestamp": 1598032410, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274799, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: 请问范老师全名是什么？哪个学院的。有上课时间地点吗", "timestamp": 1598053868, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 290002, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "范大邯老师，人文学院哲学系的。上课时间地点我之后查到了再告诉你", "timestamp": 1598539037, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 349489, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "德国古典哲学6B204 周一第六节；康德哲学与黑格尔哲学 6A211 周三第六节", "timestamp": 1600069058, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1852275, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 53100, "reply_to": 274734, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 求问范老师讲康德怎么样，任务量和给分呢\n", "timestamp": 1623673810, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 22, "pid": 53100, "reply": 22, "tag": null, "text": "本人哲学小白，存粹理性批判 存在与时间\n压根看不懂，历史书书籍史记 资治通鉴也看不进去 怎么办？\n求大佬指点迷津 自己书底子太薄了", "timestamp": 1598017782, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1623673808, "url": "", "vote": {}}}